channel.title: Initializing a method from a different class trough tabs
channel.description:
What I'm currently using in client.java [code] setSidebarInterface(14, 24999); [/code]
What I need something like this:
[code] setSidebarInterface(14, Interfacemethod()); [/code]
The thing is the interfacemethod requires the client variable c but I'm already in client.java so that's not possible? I know that setSidebarInterface probably won't work in this scenario because it requires 2 ID's. Any suggestion on what I should do?
The tab I'm opening is the achievements tab (green quest logo).
"FIXED" used process and logout.
